<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Friday was the 19th anniversary of the terrorist attacks by al-Qaeda on the United States.</p>

<p>And Kaia Gerber's new boyfriend Jacob Elordi seemed to give a nod to 9/11 as he wore a Peace Is Power sweatshirt after visiting a NYC gym.</p>

<p>The 19-year-old Vogue supermodel and the 23-year-old Euphoria actor were holding hands again after putting on their first public display of affection on their way to dinner earlier this week.</p>

